35
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,720
How powerful exactly?

36
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,360
How powerful?

37
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:35,160
It would be best if I could
transcend the tribulation,

38
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,560
master celestial arts,

39
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,280
shatter stars with a single palm

40
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,460
and split the sky with my sword energy,

41
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:44,560
as a celestial being
capable of creating illusory realm.

42
00:02:47,160 --> 00:02:49,400
Wouldn't that be a bit too fantastical?

43
00:02:50,400 --> 00:02:53,200
I'm sure you can fulfill my wish.

44
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:54,560
I beg of you.

45
00:03:02,480 --> 00:03:03,000
Ziqi,

46
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,480
could you make me

47
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:05,840
the number one beauty

48
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,680
in the sequel?

49
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:10,720
Can you make me
the supreme martial artist?

50
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:13,600
I want to have eight wives in the sequel

51
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,520
since I've never married in real life.

52
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,880
I don't need anything special,

53
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:18,280
just make me filthy rich.

54
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:20,560
Just make me the sect leader
in the sequel.

55
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,490
I'd be satisfied being the emperor
in the sequel.

56
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:36,120
(All you need to do
is lure Xiao Ziqi to a secluded spot.)

57
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,600
(Someone will take care of the rest.)

58
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,360
(Why don't I just trick him)

59
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:47,450
(by saying I want to talk to him
about how to write the sequel?)

60
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,440
(I'll do it.)

61
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:57,560
(Any more suggestions,)

62
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,590
(I'll abandon writing.)

63
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,240
Alright.

64
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,800
