72
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,400
She eventually defeated the villains

73
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,360
and reclaimed Changliu Mountain.

74
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,080
Good.

75
00:04:33,300 --> 00:04:34,780
You've tied up the loose ends nicely.

76
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,240
Well written. Just keep writing.

77
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:40,280
From now on, our Changliu Sect
will be known

78
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:43,480
as a righteous and noble sect.

79
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:44,920
And I'll be

80
00:04:45,280 --> 00:04:47,280
the lovable heroine admired by all,

81
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,600
roaming the world

82
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:50,960
with my sword.

83
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,920
- Yes, exactly.
- Yes.

84
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,720
Great minds think alike.

85
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,960
We think alike.

86
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:25,300
