96
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,400
Exactly.

97
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:48,040
I told you, the wedding wasn't in vain.

98
00:05:48,060 --> 00:05:49,920
Changliu Sect's luck
is finally turning around.

99
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,160
So, should we perform a few more times?

100
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,640
Maybe our luck will reach the heavens.

101
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:54,840
No way.

102
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,120
When the moon is full, it wanes.

103
00:05:57,880 --> 00:05:59,560
It's best not to push our luck too far.

104
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:00,960
Alright.

105
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:03,400
Well, since our luck is good right now,

106
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:05,200
