new disciples tomorrow.

107
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:07,790
It's been a long time
since we last recruited.

108
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,520
My father would be
very pleased to know this.

109
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:13,920
Recruit more handsome men.

110
00:06:19,780 --> 00:06:22,140
