111
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:23,920
Five taels of silver.

112
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,280
This is top-quality goods.

113
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,160
Five taels of silver.

114
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,560
