121
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,160
Everyone, please be patient.

122
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,720
There's plenty for everyone.

123
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,480
Alright.

124
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,720
