128
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,800
Please, go ahead.

129
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,040
Well,

130
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,720
we've

131
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:04,240
leased out

132
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,400
a storefront for a restaurant.

133
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,580
But it's been several months
and we haven't received any rent.

134
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,600
I'm not very good at accounting,

135
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,720
so I was hoping you could

136
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,920
help me to check it out.

137
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,800
It's not far from here.

138
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:18,000
(He must be up to something.
I'll go see.)

139
00:07:18,280 --> 00:07:19,040
Alright,

140
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,480
