141
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,280
Thank you.

142
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,400
You're welcome.

143
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:27,960
Well...

144
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:29,520
