like that with Liu Yimei.

179
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:54,880
If Xuefu hadn't told me you were gone,

180
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,460
I would've...

181
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,960
Were you planning to spend the night

182
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,960
