suddenly so close to him?

204
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:50,000
Well...

205
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,840
Lipei.

206
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,200
Lipei.

207
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:55,280
Lipei.

